1719}
1720
1721static inline bool setJSHTMLElement_styleSetter(JSGlobalObject& lexicalGlobalObject, JSHTMLElement& thisObject, JSValue value)
1722{
1723 auto& vm = JSC::getVM(&lexicalGlobalObject);
1724 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
1725 auto id = Identifier::fromString(vm, reinterpret_cast<const LChar*>("style"), strlen("style"));
1726 auto valueToForwardTo = thisObject.get(&lexicalGlobalObject, id);
1727 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, false);
1728 if (UNLIKELY(!valueToForwardTo.isObject())) {
1729 throwTypeError(&lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope);
1730 return false;
1731 }
1732 auto forwardId = Identifier::fromString(vm, reinterpret_cast<const LChar*>("cssText"), strlen("cssText"));
1733 PutPropertySlot slot(valueToForwardTo, false);
1734 asObject(valueToForwardTo)->methodTable(vm)->put(asObject(valueToForwardTo), &lexicalGlobalObject, forwardId, value, slot);
1735 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, false);
1736 return true;
1737}
1738

1742}

4619static inline bool setJSHTMLElement_tabIndexSetter(JSGlobalObject& lexicalGlobalObject, JSHTMLElement& thisObject, JSValue value)
4620{
4621 auto& vm = JSC::getVM(&lexicalGlobalObject);
4622 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
4623 CustomElementReactionStack customElementReactionStack(lexicalGlobalObject);
4624 auto& impl = thisObject.wrapped();
4625 auto nativeValue = convert<IDLLong>(lexicalGlobalObject, value);
4626 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, false);
4627 invokeFunctorPropagatingExceptionIfNecessary(lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope, [&] {
4628 return impl.setTabIndexForBindings(WTFMove(nativeValue));
4629 });
4630 return true;
4631}

4686JSC::IsoSubspace* JSHTMLElement::subspaceForImpl(JSC::VM& vm)
4687{
4688 auto& clientData = *static_cast<JSVMClientData*>(vm.clientData);
4689 auto& spaces = clientData.subspaces();
4690 if (auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLElement.get())
4691 return space;
4692 static_assert(std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSHTMLElement> || !JSHTMLElement::needsDestruction);
4693 if constexpr (std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSHTMLElement>)
4694 spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.destructibleObjectHeapCellType.get(), JSHTMLElement);
4695 else
4696 spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.cellHeapCellType.get(), JSHTMLElement);
4697 auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLElement.get();
4698IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("unreachable-code")
4699IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("tautological-compare")
4700 void (*myVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSHTMLElement::visitOutputConstraints;
4701 void (*jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSC::JSCell::visitOutputConstraints;
4702 if (myVisitOutputConstraint != jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)
4703 clientData.outputConstraintSpaces().append(space);
4704IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
4705IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
4706 return space;
4707}
